.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, cucumber, kiwi, pineapple
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, hedgehog, pony
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | pineapple | kiwi | cucumber | cauliflower |
| Pet    | dog       | pony | hedgehog | hamster     |

