.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, indie, salsa
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, mouse, rat
1. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
3. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | indie | electronic | classical | salsa  |
| Pet           | mouse | chinchilla | rat       | ferret |

