.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, designer, entrepreneur, musician
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, tram, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the designer##1
2. the person driving the trike is the musician##1
3. the designer is on the right of the chef##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the car is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | entrepreneur | chef      | designer | musician |
| Transport   | car          | quad-bike | tram     | trike    |

