.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, taxi, train, tram
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | cola | milk  | hot-chocolate | sprite |
| Transport   | tram | train | taxi          | bus    |

