.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, mexican, nigerian
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, scooter, snowmobile
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the american is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the nigerian is the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | american | mexican | argentine | nigerian   |
| Transport     | scooter  | boat    | car       | snowmobile |

